- if current_user.tips_shown
  #gs_container.js_tips_container
    #getting_started_title
      %h2= "Getting started with Activity Splits"
      = render :partial => 'shared/tips_hide'
    .getting_started
      .message
        %p Use Activity splits to conveniently add several dimensions of detail to your Activities.
        %ul.bulleted
          %li Enter the Input(s) (Cost Categories) you used
          %li Show the Purpose(s) for the Activity. The more specific the Purposes you enter, the easier it will be to generate reports for you!
          %li Add your allocation of resources to each Location.
          %li If your Activity is more complex, you can add as much detail as you like with more Inputs/Purposes etc.
